================================================================================
  DESCRIPTION (4000 characters max)
================================================================================

  UNJYNX is the task manager that refuses to let you forget. While every other
  app relies on push notifications you have trained yourself to ignore, UNJYNX
  sends reminders directly to WhatsApp, Telegram, Instagram, SMS, Discord,
  Slack, and Email. Your tasks follow you to the platforms you actually check.

  REMINDERS THAT ACTUALLY WORK

  Set a task. Choose your channels. UNJYNX handles the rest. If you miss a
  WhatsApp reminder, it escalates to SMS. Still no response? It can follow up
  on Telegram. You configure the escalation chain. UNJYNX makes sure nothing
  slips through.

  Seven channels. One mission: never let you miss what matters.

  GHOST MODE -- DEEP FOCUS, UNLOCKED

  When you need to lock in, Ghost Mode blocks distractions and tells your team
  you are unavailable. A built-in Pomodoro timer with ambient soundscapes --
  rain on a window, a bustling cafe, a quiet forest -- keeps you in flow state.
  Your notifications wait. Your focus does not.

  PROGRESS THAT MOTIVATES

  UNJYNX tracks your productivity like a fitness app tracks your runs. Daily
  streak rings, contribution heatmaps, personal bests, and weekly AI insights
  turn task completion into something you actually want to maintain. Watch your
  consistency build day after day.

  DAILY WISDOM

  Begin each day with curated content from 60+ categories. Ancient wisdom from
  the Mahabharata. Stoic philosophy from Marcus Aurelius. Creative fire from
  Stan Lee. Entrepreneurial grit from modern founders. Build a morning ritual
  that sharpens your mind before the first task.

  SMART SCHEDULING

  AI learns when you do your best work. It suggests optimal times for creative
  tasks, admin work, and deep thinking based on your energy patterns. Stop
  fighting your natural rhythm -- work with it.

  TEAMS THAT SHIP

  Shared workspaces, delegated tasks, team analytics, custom notification
  policies, SSO integration, and admin controls. UNJYNX Team is built for
  groups that need to execute, not just communicate.

  OFFLINE-FIRST ARCHITECTURE

  Everything works without an internet connection. Create tasks, complete them,
  take notes -- it all syncs seamlessly when you reconnect. Field-level
  conflict resolution means no data loss, ever.

  PRIVACY BY DESIGN

  Your data is encrypted in transit with TLS 1.3 and at rest on our servers.
  We comply with India's Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023. Request
  full data deletion at any time -- we honor it within 30 days.

  PRICING

  Free: 25 tasks, push notifications, 1 project, daily wisdom.
  Pro: USD 6.99/mo (USD 4.99/mo annual) -- unlimited tasks, all 7 channels,
  Ghost Mode, AI scheduling, full analytics.
  Team: USD 8.99/user/mo (USD 6.99/user/mo annual) -- everything in Pro plus
  workspaces, team analytics, SSO, API access.

  No hidden fees. No surprise charges. Cancel anytime from your Apple ID
  subscription settings.

  FROM THE MAKERS

  UNJYNX is crafted by METAminds with obsessive attention to detail. Beautiful
  Material 3 design. Smooth 60fps animations. Dark mode with midnight purple
  and electric gold. Light mode with a soft purple-mist palette.

  Break the satisfactory. Unjynx your productivity.

  Character count: ~3500/4000

