  - Ghost Mode: deep focus with Pomodoro timer and ambient sounds
  - Progress Dashboard: streaks, heatmaps, personal bests, weekly insights
  - Daily Wisdom: curated content from 60+ categories
  - Morning Rituals: start your day with intention
  - Offline-first: works without internet, syncs when reconnected
  - Beautiful design: Material 3, dark and light themes, smooth animations

  We would love your feedback. Reach us at support@unjynx.app.

================================================================================
  REVIEW NOTES FOR APPLE REVIEWER
================================================================================

  Dear App Review Team,

  Thank you for reviewing UNJYNX. Here are notes to help with the review:

  PURPOSE:
  UNJYNX is a task management and reminder application. Its primary
  differentiator is sending reminders through external messaging platforms
  (WhatsApp, Telegram, Instagram, SMS, Discord, Slack, Email) in addition to
  standard push notifications.

  ACCOUNT CREATION:
  Users sign up with email/password or social login (Google, Apple Sign-In).
  Authentication is handled via Logto (self-hosted OIDC provider). No phone
  number is required for basic account creation.

  MULTI-CHANNEL REMINDERS:
  The app connects to messaging platforms via their official APIs:
  - WhatsApp: Gupshup Business Solution Provider (official Meta partner)
  - Telegram: Official Bot API
  - Instagram: Official Messenger API
  - SMS: MSG91 (licensed telecom aggregator)
  - Discord: Official Discord Bot API
  - Slack: Official Slack Web API
  - Email: SendGrid

  Users must explicitly opt in and verify each channel before receiving
  reminders. WhatsApp and SMS require OTP verification.

  IN-APP PURCHASES:
  - Pro plan: USD 6.99/month or USD 59.88/year (auto-renewable subscription)
  - Team plan: USD 8.99/user/month or USD 83.88/user/year (auto-renewable)
  - Family plan: USD 9.99/month (auto-renewable, up to 5 members)
  Subscriptions are managed via RevenueCat and processed through StoreKit.
  Users can cancel anytime from their Apple ID settings.

  DEMO ACCOUNT:
  Email:    reviewer@unjynx.app
  Password: AppReview2026!

  This account has Pro features enabled and pre-populated with sample tasks
  to demonstrate all functionality.

  GHOST MODE:
  This is a focus timer feature. It does NOT block system notifications at
  the OS level. It only mutes UNJYNX notifications and shows a focus timer
  UI within the app. The app uses no private APIs.

  BACKGROUND ACTIVITY:
  The app uses background fetch to sync tasks when connectivity returns.
  No background audio, location, or VoIP usage.

  DATA HANDLING:
  - Data collected: name, email, task content, device info (for push tokens)
  - Data encrypted: TLS 1.3 in transit, AES-256 at rest
  - Data shared with third parties: None (backend is self-hosted)
  - DPDP Act 2023 compliant
  - User can request data deletion from Settings > Privacy > Delete Account

  CONTENT:
  Daily wisdom quotes are curated and pre-moderated. No user-generated
  content is displayed to other users. Task data is private to the user
  (or shared within a team workspace with explicit invitation).

  If you have any questions, please contact us at review@unjynx.app.

  Best regards,
  METAminds Development Team

